#: characters/templates/characters/fragments/advancement.html:12
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Reputation represents the popularity of a character. Reputation "
"can be\n"
"            to purchase new character templates. Reputation is distributed "
"by the GM after each game session and for\n"
"            special events.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Die Reputation entspricht der Beliebtheit eines Charakters. Reputation kann\n"
"zum Kauf neuer Charakterschablonen verwendet werden. Die Reputation wird vom "
"Spielleiter nach jeder Spielsitzung und bei\n"
"besondere Ereignisse\n"
"  "

#: characters/templates/characters/fragments/advancement.html:19
msgid "Your gained reputation is"
msgstr "Deine erhaltene Reputation ist"

#: characters/templates/characters/fragments/advancement.html:29
