msgid "Lose Grace"
msgstr "Gunst verlieren"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:12
msgid "-Grace"
msgstr "-Gunst"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:18
msgid "Gain Grace"
msgstr "Gunst erlangen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:18
msgid "+Grace"
msgstr "+Gunst"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:30
msgid "Reduce Attitude"
msgstr "Gesinnung verringern"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:30
msgid "-Attitude"
msgstr "-Gesinnung"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:36
msgid "Increase Attitude"
msgstr "Gesinnung erhöhen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:36
msgid "+Attitude"
msgstr "+Gesinnung"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:62
msgid ""
"You can receive grace by doing things for your deity, or act on their behalf."
msgstr ""
"Du kannst Gunst erhalten, wenn du Dinge für deine Gottheit tust, oder in "
"ihrem Sinne handelst."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/grace.html:69
msgid ""
"Attitude describes the basic orientation of your character. The value ranges "
"from 1 to 100, where 1 stands for abysmally evil, 100 for exceptionally good-"
"natured."
msgstr ""
"Gesinnung beschreibt die grundlegende Ausrichtung deines Charakters. Der "
"Wert reicht von 1 bis 100, wobei 1 für abgrundtief böse, 100 für "
"außerordentlich gutmütig steht."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:23
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:28
msgid "Base Stress"
msgstr "Basisstress"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:35
msgid "Heal Quirk"
msgstr "Eigenart heilen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:40
msgid "Gain Quirk"
msgstr "Eigenart erlangen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:46
msgid "Stress Test"
msgstr "Stresstest"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:47
msgid "Willpower + Logic"
msgstr "Willenskraft + Logik"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:48
msgid "Roll Stress Test"
msgstr "Stresstest würfeln"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:77
msgid ""
"\n"
"      Your base stress level is a measure of how much exposure you have had "
"to the horrors of the world.\n"
"      Your stress level cannot fall below your base stress level.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Dein Basisstress ist ein Maß dafür, wie sehr du den Schrecken der Welt "
"ausgesetzt warst.\n"
"Dein Stresslevel kann nicht unter deinen Basisstress fallen.\n"
"    "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:86
msgid ""
"\n"
"      Your current stress level. If it reaches your stress maximum,\n"
"      you will gain the condition <i>Consumed by dread</i>.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   Dein aktueller Stresslevel. Wenn es dein Stressmaximum erreicht,\n"
"   erhälst du den Zustand <i>von Grauen erfasst</i>.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:95
msgid ""
"\n"
"      This is the possible stress you can cope with.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dies ist der mögliche Stress, mit dem du umgehen kannst.\n"
"    "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:102
msgid "Your quirks"
msgstr "Deine Eigenarten"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:107
msgid ""
"\n"
"          You gained a not yet chosen quirk due to stress. Choose a\n"
"          Quirk from the list of available quirks or create a new one.\n"
"          Consult your Gamemaster to decide which quirk matches the\n"
"          situation.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Du hast eine Eigenart durch Stress bekommen, die du noch nicht gewählt "
"hast. \n"
"Wähle eine Eigenart aus der Liste der verfügbaren eigenarten oder erstelle "
"eine neue.\n"
"Sprich dich mit deinem Spielleiter ab, welche Eigenart am besten zur "
"Situation passt.\n"
"    "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:148
msgid "Remove Quirk"
msgstr "Eigenart entfernen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/horror.html:154
msgid "You don't have any quirks."
msgstr "Du hast keine Eigenarten."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/item.html:18
msgid "Less"
msgstr "Weniger"

