#: portal/templates/portal/_navigation.html:48
msgid "More"
msgstr "Mehr"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/item.html:119
msgid "Put into container"
msgstr "In Container legen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:10
msgid "Use Arcana"
msgstr "Arkana benutzen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:10
msgid "-Arcana"
msgstr "-Arkana"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:15
msgid "Restore Arcana"
msgstr "Arkana wiederherstellen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:15
msgid "+Arcana"
msgstr "+Arkana"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:38
msgid "An arcana slot, which can be used to cast spells."
msgstr "Ein Arkana, das für Zauber benutzt werden kann."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:41
msgid "Used Arcana"
msgstr "Benutztes Arkana"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/magic.html:44
msgid "A used arcane slot. This can be refreshed taking a rest."
msgstr "Ein benutztes Arkana. Dies kann durch eine Rast aufgefrischt werden."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/note.html:25
msgid "Save Note"
msgstr "Notiz speichern"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/note.html:30
msgid "Delete Note"
msgstr "Notiz Löschen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/protection.html:53
msgid "Restore all"
msgstr "Alle wiederherstellen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/protection.html:54
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Click on the shield icons above to spend protection points.\n"
"        You can spend protection points whenever a hit is taken and not "
"otherwise prevented.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Klicke auf die Schildsymbole oben, um Schutzpunkte auszugeben.\n"
"Du kannst immer dann Schutzpunkte ausgeben, wenn du einen Treffer hinnehmen "
"musst und dieser nicht anderweitig verhindert werden kann.\n"
"    "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/protection.html:64
#: discretion/settings.py:324
msgid "Protection Types"
msgstr "Schutztypen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/protection.html:75
msgid ""
"\n"
"        This is an innate protection that comes from your character's "
"lineage. Unlike the other protection types, this\n"
"        protection does not deplete until the end of combat; it refreshes at "
"the start of the player's combat round.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Dieser angeborene Schutz stammt aus der Abstammung des Charakters. Im "
"Gegensatz zu den anderen Schutzarten bleibt dieser nicht bis zum Ende des "
"Kampfes aufgebraucht, sondern wird zu Beginn jeder Kampfrunde des Spielers "
"erneuert.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/quirk.html:13
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/recipe.html:13
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/spell.html:32
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/template.html:13
msgid "Forget"
msgstr "Vergessen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/reputation.html:6
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Reputation represents the characters degree of popularity. "
"Reputation may be\n"
"        spent to get new character templates.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Die Reputation gibt den Bekanntheitsgrad des Charakters an. Reputation kann\n"
"für den Erwerb neuer Charakterschablonen ausgegeben werden.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/reputation.html:12
msgid ""
"\n"
"        The game master distributes reputation after each game session and "
"for\n"
"        special events.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Der Spielleiter verteilt die Reputation nach jeder Spielsitzung und bei\n"
"besonderen Ereignissen.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/reputation.html:60
msgid ""
"\n"
"            You have unspent reputation points. Use them to add new "
"templates to your\n"
"            character and advance in your professions.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Du hast noch nicht ausgegebene Reputation. Nutze sie, um deinem\n"
"Charakter hinzuzufügen und in deinen Berufen aufzusteigen.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/riot_gear.html:15
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:38
msgid "Repair"
msgstr "Reparieren"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/riot_gear.html:36
msgid "Is equipped"
msgstr "Ist ausgerüstet"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/riot_gear.html:56
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        This shield provides %(t_cover)s cover. Roll a d6 for each hit, a "
"success prevents that hit.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"     Dieses Schild bietet %(t_cover)s Deckung. Wirf für jeden Treffer einen "
"W6, jeder Erfolg verhindert den jeweiligen Treffer.\n"
"     "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/riot_gear.html:66
msgid "Shield Cover"
msgstr "Schilddeckung"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/riot_gear.html:112
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:98
