#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/spell.html:23
#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:51
msgid "Add Modification"
msgstr "Modifikatoren hinzufügen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/spell.html:46
msgid "Spell cost"
msgstr "Zauber Kosten"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/spell.html:57
#: magic/templates/magic/_basespell_widget.html:24
#: magic/templates/magic/basespell_detail.html:39
#: rulebook/templates/rulebook/pdf/appendix/spells.html:21
msgid "Spell Casting"
msgstr "Zaubern"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/template.html:28
#: rulebook/templates/rulebook/pdf/appendix/templates.html:22
#: rules/templates/rules/_template_widget.html:17
msgid "Allows to perform the acts of a priest."
msgstr "Erlaubt es, die Handlungen eines Priesters auszuführen."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:12
msgid "Attack:"
msgstr "Angriff:"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:24
msgid "Reload"
msgstr "Nachladen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:89
msgid "Ammunition"
msgstr "Munition"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weapon.html:140
msgid "Remove Modification"
msgstr "Modifikatoren entfernen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weaponless.html:12
msgid "Attack"
msgstr "Angriff"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weaponless.html:19
msgid ""
"\n"
"          If the character attacks without a weapon, the player rolls hit "
"dice equal to his Hand to hand combat value.\n"
"          The minimum roll is equal to the character's minimum roll, which "
"is usually 5+.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\t\tGreift der Character ohne Waffe an, so wirft der Spieler Trefferwürfel "
"entsprechend seinem Wert Nahkampf. Der Mindestwurf entspricht dem "
"Mindestwurf des Charakters, also in der Regel 5+.\n"
"\t"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weaponless.html:25
msgid ""
"\n"
"          If the character's Strength value is higher than 2, the successful "
"attack gains piercing 1.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\t\tIst der Wert Kraft des Charakters höher als 2, so verursacht der "
"erfolgreiche Angriff 1 Durchschlag.\n"
"\t"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/weaponless.html:30
msgid ""
"\n"
"          If the character's Quickness value is higher than 2, the character "
"adds one die to the roll.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\t\tIst der Wert Schnelligkeit des Charakters höher als 2, so fügt der "
"Charakter dem Wurf einen Würfel hinzu. \n"
"\t"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:47
msgid "Status effects"
msgstr "Statuseffekte"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:49
msgid ""
"\n"
"      Status effects apply over time. Each status effect has a rule for when "
"it expires from the character.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\tStatuseffekte gelten über Zeit. Jeder Statuseffekt hat eine Regel, wann er "
"vom Charakter abfällt.\n"
"  "

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:84
msgid "Wound Types"
msgstr "Wundentypen"

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:89
msgid "A full heart. This can compensate a wound."
msgstr "Ein volles Herz. Dieses kann eine Wunde kompensieren."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:95
msgid "A wound taken. This empty heart can be restored taking a rest."
msgstr ""
"Eine hingenommene Wunde. Dieses leere Herz kann bei einer Rast "
"wiederhergestellt werden."

#: characters/templates/characters/sidebar/wounds.html:101
msgid ""
"A temporary boost, given by special equipment or magic. If you take damage "
"this will expended first."
msgstr ""
"Ein zeitweiser Boost, kann durch spezielle Ausrüstung oder Magie erhalten "
"werden. Wenn du Schaden nimmst wird dieses zuerst entfernt."

