#: portal/templates/portal/yearly_wrapup.html:11
#: portal/templates/portal/yearly_wrapup.html:25
#, python-format
msgid "%(t_year)s in Review"
msgstr "Jahresrückblick %(t_year)s"

#: characters/templates/index.html:14
msgid "Click here"
msgstr "Hier klicken"

#: characters/templates/index.html:23
msgid "Logo"
msgstr "Logo"

#: characters/templates/index.html:32
#: rulebook/templates/rulebook/download.html:5
#: rulebook/templates/rulebook/download.html:6
msgid "Download rulebook"
msgstr "Regelbuch herunterladen"

#: characters/templates/index.html:41
msgid "Lead Image"
msgstr "Seitenbild"

#: characters/templates/index.html:54
msgid "Create Characters"
msgstr "Charaktere erstellen"

#: characters/templates/index.html:56
msgid ""
"\n"
"            This website lets you create and manage your characters as well "
"as their equipment\n"
"            and possessions. This makes it really easy to use a platform "
"like\n"
"            <a href=\"https://roll20.net\">Roll20</a> for your sessions.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Auf dieser Webseite kannst du deine Charaktere erstellen und verwalten, "
"zudem ihre Ausrüstung\n"
"und ihren Besitz. Das macht es einfach Plattformen wie \n"
"<a href=\"https://roll20.net\">Roll20</a> für deine Sitzungen zu benutzen.\n"
" "

#: characters/templates/index.html:91
msgid "Manage Campaigns"
msgstr "Kampagnen verwalten"

#: characters/templates/index.html:93
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Create and manage your campaigns. Invite your friends to join "
"and play with you.\n"
"            You can also add enemies and foes to your campaign to keep track "
"of them. Dice rolls\n"
"            may be sent to discord.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"     Erstelle und verwalte deine Kampagnen. Lade Freunde ein, der Kampagne "
"beizutreten.\n"
"     Du kannst auch Feinde und NPC hinzufügen, um diese zu verwalten. "
"Würfelwürfe\n"
"     können an Discord gesendet werden.\n"
"   "

#: characters/templates/index.html:132
msgid "Discover the world"
msgstr "Entdecke die Welt"

#: characters/templates/index.html:152 characters/templates/index.html:180
#: worlds/templates/worlds/world_list.html:21
msgid "Discover"
msgstr "Entdecken"

#: characters/templates/index.html:165
msgid "Discover worlds"
msgstr "Entdecke Welten"

#: characters/templates/index.html:166
msgid "Play in one of these worlds, or use Terra to play on earth."
msgstr ""
"Spiele in einer dieser Welten, oder wähle Terra, um auf der Erde zu spielen."

#: characters/templates/index.html:195
msgid "Open Source Role Playing Game"
msgstr "OpenSource Rollenspiel"

#: characters/templates/index.html:198
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"              <em>%(t_brand_name)s</em> is an open source role playing game "
"that is free to use, copy and modify.\n"
"              The content, rules and code are all available, licensed under "
"CC-BY-NC-SA, GPL and CC0 license.\n"
"              Find out more on the <a href=\"%(t_contact_url)s\">contact "
"page</a>.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<em>%(t_brand_name)s</em> ist ein Open-Source-Rollenspiel, das frei "
"verwendet, kopiert und verändert werden kann.\n"
"Der Inhalt, die Regeln und der Code sind alle verfügbar, lizenziert unter CC-"
"BY-NC-SA, GPL und CC0 Lizenz.\n"
"Weitere Informationen findest du auf der <a "
"href=\"%(t_contact_url)s\">Kontaktseite</a>.\n"
"      "

#: characters/views.py:98
msgid "Character cloned. You are now viewing the duplicate."
msgstr "Charakter geklont. Du siehst nun die Kopie."

#: characters/views.py:118
msgid "Character deleted."
msgstr "Charakter gelöscht."

#: characters/views.py:242
msgid "Rest wound roll"
msgstr "Rastwundenwurf"

#: characters/views.py:243
msgid "Wound roll"
msgstr "Wundenwurf"

#: characters/views.py:258
msgid "Rest arcana roll"
msgstr "Rastarkanawurf"

#: characters/views.py:259
msgid "Arcana roll"
msgstr "Arkanawurf"

#: characters/views.py:273
msgid "Rest resolve dread"
msgstr "Grauen auflösen"

#: characters/views.py:274
msgid "Resolve dread roll"
msgstr "Grauen auflösen Wurf"

#: characters/views.py:727
msgid "Choose a suitable name for your character."
msgstr "Wähle einen passenden Namen für deinen Charakter."

#: characters/views.py:752
msgid ""
"At several places in the interface, your character will be referred to using "
"their pronouns. Choose the pronouns that best describe your character."
msgstr ""
"An verschiedenen Stellen wird dein Charakter mit Pronomen angesprochen. "
"Wähle die Pronomen, die am besten passen."

#: characters/views.py:760
msgid "Enter the birthdate of your character."
msgstr "Gib das Geburtsdatum deines Charakters ein."

#: characters/views.py:767
msgid ""
"Specify a starting capital for your character. The seed money is usually\n"
"            defined by the game master and determines how much equipment the "
"character can have at the\n"
"            beginning of the game."
msgstr ""
"Gib ein Startkapital für deinen Charakter an. Das Startkapital wird in der "
"Regel\n"
"       vom Spielleiter festgelegt und bestimmt, wie viel Ausrüstung der "
"Charakter zu\n"
"      Beginn des Spiels haben kann."

#: characters/views.py:785
msgid ""
"The attitude indicates the morality of the character. The value ranges\n"
"            from 0 to 100, with an attitude of 0 corresponding to a deeply "
"evil character and a value of 100\n"
"            corresponding to a good character. The value is freely "
